com.polarion.alm.shared.api.model.document

Interface DocumentWorkItems

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<WorkItem>, IterableWithSize<WorkItem>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    UpdatableDocumentWorkItems

    public interface DocumentWorkItems
extends IterableWithSize<WorkItem>
    Iterating over this instances iterates over all Work Items from the document (even the unreferenced).
    Since:
    3.9.0
